plot: Toni and Maria had been dating for a long time and, suddenly, they decide to get married. The decision don't sits well with Toni's parents, Poppins and Rosa, two ex-hippies that never married and that are the proud owners of a sex shop. Crazyness ensues, and finally Toni and Maria end up married... and living in his parent's spare flat over the sex shop. Their over-sexed best friends, Calafell (who's also the owner of the hotel Maria works at) and Rosa (Toni's fellow teacher) add to the general mayhem of their lives.   Written by  LadyAndy
title: L'un per l'altre
